Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.95,0:01:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天我们要来研究深海轻柔的韵律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today we study the gentle rhythm of the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻柔的韵律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gentle rhythm
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.86,0:01:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.86,0:01:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ocean wave
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热带浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:33.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tropical waves
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.00,0:01:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whirlpool
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反向漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reverse whirlpool
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  把那噪音关了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, turn that noise off
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吹一下  他多半就能注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This will get his attention
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你又把自己竖笛给吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you swallowed your clarinet again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.04,0:02:08.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来取
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:08.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.65,0:02:09.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:09.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.67,0:02:10.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:10.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.68,0:02:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.68,0:02:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,touch
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.62,0:02:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得再仔细看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get a better look
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.19,0:02:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too dark
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以就要采取极端措施
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This calls for extreme measures
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.80,0:02:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,取出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.80,0:02:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,末端尖尖的那块不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pointy bit on the end is missing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个叫做簧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's called a reed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.12,0:02:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么叫做簧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a reed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下可好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的簧片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My reed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.92,0:02:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is still
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.57,0:02:39.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡在我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:39.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stuck in my
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.14,0:02:40.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喉咙里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:40.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,throat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's all your fault
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩一个办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one thing to do
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须去找珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to see Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.45,0:02:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你竖笛末端尖尖的那块
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got that pointy bit from the end of your clarinet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.64,0:02:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡到你喉咙里了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stuck in your throat
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可真是笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was clumsy of you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是海绵宝宝他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.27,0:02:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was SpongeBob that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也没别的办法了  必须动手术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there's nothing to do for it but surgery
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在正好可以来试试我的新发明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now is my chance to try out my new invention--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以用它来解决你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the solution to your problem
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一艘潜艇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A submarine?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来给你展示一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me show you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这一整间实验室叫做缩小室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This whole lab is called the Chamber of Shrinkage
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到时我会把自己跟潜艇缩到微观尺度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll shrink the sub and myself down to microscopic size
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着航行穿越你的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then navigate through your brain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路开进你的喉咙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down into your throat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从里面取出簧片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and extract the reed from inside
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Simple
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么不干脆缩小簧片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just shrink the reed?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老是想着搞费力不讨好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,always wanting to do it the hard way
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都就绪了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all set, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好打镇静剂了没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready for the sedative?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定这样安全吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is safe?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全安全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Completely
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要驾驶员很靠谱就行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as someone competent is behind the wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.95,0:03:52.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你做个好梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:52.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams, pardner
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘了给这趟航行打包食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot to pack food for the trip
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得去我树屋拿点补给品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:57.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to get some supplies from my treedome
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不在时  你们负责看守潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I need you to guard the submarine while I'm gone
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得自己办得到吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can handle it, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,办得到  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can do, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.80,0:04:09.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  市民
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:09.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, citizen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看守珊迪的潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guarding Sandy's submarine
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.07,0:04:17.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来就没进过潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:17.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never been in a submarine
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's look inside
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还在看守呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm guarding it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:21.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, man
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能进去看守吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could you guard it from the inside?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you're a genius
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:28.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,824)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝和派大星前来报到看守
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Patrick reporting for guard duty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(902,464)}缩小
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,缩小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Shrink"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:47.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(720,920)}精神病医生
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑子确实一堆毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:50.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do have a lot of issues
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm back, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你变得好小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're so tiny
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好大一个海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A giant SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.90,0:05:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪长得特别大一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's grown to gigantic size
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该不是珊迪长大了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think Sandy grew, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是我们缩小了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we shrunk
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's silly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就不觉得更有可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's more likely
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整个世界都长大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that the entire world grew?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.62,0:05:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  潜艇已经安全进入你体内了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the submarine is safely inside you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonderful
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这外面  那谁在开潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you're out here, then who's in here?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还是亲眼看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you take a look for yourself?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.91,0:05:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝和派大星在我脑袋开小潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Patrick are piloting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a miniature submarine inside my head
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝和派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:57.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:05:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好冷静一点  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:11.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better calm down, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们既然都进了你的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With them little critters inside you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就千万别老是乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be moving around too much
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然会被他们撞到要害的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can knock them into something important
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.92,0:06:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  可这里乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but it's a real dump
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听得到我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can you hear me?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来救你了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll save you, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  你们俩小不点白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you itty-bitty idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们这是在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这是非法闯入  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're trespassing, SpongeBob--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闯进了我实验室  我潜艇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in my lab, my submarine--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还闯入了章鱼哥的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you're trespassing inside of Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老觉得这地方样子烂透了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought this place was in bad shape
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.27,0:06:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I heard that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是把你带出去吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get you out of there, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要找到自动驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is locate the autopilot
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.90,0:06:56.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就能安全带你完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:56.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll safely take you through your mission
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后从撤离点撤出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then out the extraction point
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We broke it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害死他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kill him?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这东西比船还难开17倍左右
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is approximately 17 times harder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:11.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to drive than a boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而你从来就没成功开过船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which you're never successfully done
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以千万不要激动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So just take it nice and easy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problemo
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice and
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:21.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,easy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, how's it going?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我控制不住自己眼球了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't control my eyeballs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一会儿就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's temporary
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在签下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, just sign this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(458,486)}豁免声明
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.41,0:07:54.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:54.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.72,0:07:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单纯签个名而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just your autograph
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.07,0:07:58.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留着等你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:58.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for when you're, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.39,0:07:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:07:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,famous
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.39,0:08:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有大头照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got headshots, you know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:04.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:05.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.39,0:08:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快还来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, give it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快还来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it back
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们在撞你中枢神经系统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're hitting your central nervous system
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.00,0:08:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的动作已经失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not in control of your actions
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.94,0:08:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的动作已经失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not in control of my actions
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们偏航了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They've gone off course
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.26,0:08:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're out of control
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mayday
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mayday
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们在下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sinking
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星一直叫个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And Patrick won't stop screaming
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胃酸水平已经过高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those stomach acid levels are way too high
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,燃料储备就快要用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The reserve tanks are almost empty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finished
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  一定要逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you got to get out of there
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从胃部直接就能直达食道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a straight shot up the stomach to the esophagus
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,簧片就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:06.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where the reed is
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.28,0:09:11.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要能找到替代燃料就能完成任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can complete your mission
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if we could just access an alternative fuel
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如天然气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like natural gas
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天然气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:14.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Natural gas?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就比如这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别在我身体里打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop burping inside me
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:21.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可能有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They might be on to something
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你打嗝打得够大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:27.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you could make a big enough burp
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就可以通过压载舱过滤二氧化碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could filter the CO2 through our ballast tanks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,重新发动引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,refire the engines
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乘着冲击波逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and ride the shock wave out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就用你的办法了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going through with your plan, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.05,0:09:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What plan?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打嗝吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now burp, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经命悬一线了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lives are on the line
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没想到会是这样的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never thought it would end this way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,394)}天然气储备
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们朝着食道冲过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're heading for the esophagus
Dialogue: 1,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都吃了什么玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have you been eating?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那俩白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morons
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝呼叫珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob to Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们已经抵达异物所在处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're reached the foreign obstruction
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们得出去想办法移除它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:26.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to have to go out and dislodge it somehow
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经在移了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm already on it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:32.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,两小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这破锤子什么都砸不碎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This stupid hammer won't break anything
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  做你天生就会的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, do what you were born to do
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:43.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dance
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漩涡转
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whirlpool spin
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good work, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你们就只要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now all you have to do is
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of my body
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.55,0:11:04.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.15,0:11:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grow?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1054,196)}长大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,410)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快开门营业了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost ready to open
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(956,692)}不得退款
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.10,0:11:18.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune's trousers
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前来报到  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Reporting for duty, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.22,0:11:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  马桶又堵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, the toilet's backed up again
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.21,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FFC1&\fsp40}那不是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(245.316,450)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(495.678,728)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:39.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(377.566,404)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(503.736,656)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:44.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(856,886)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.98,0:11:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You there
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who me?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速离开镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get outta town
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速离开镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get outta town
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.60,0:12:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到美丽的晴空海岸度假区度假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And take a vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to beautiful Sunny Seashores Resort
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你吧  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(280,578)}速速\N离开镇子\N\N到美丽的\N晴空海岸\N度假区
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得速速离开镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得马上走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:22.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get going
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.23,0:12:24.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是他叫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:24.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He told me to
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who did?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不太确定  但他有个手提箱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but he had a briefcase
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手提箱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A briefcase
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他多半是个雇佣杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He might be a paid assassin
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是派大星  你不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Patrick, you can't go--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.43,0:12:45.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能就这么走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:45.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not like this
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁还能跟我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who will go with me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.75,0:12:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,参加下一届水母捕手博览会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the next Jellyfisherman's Expo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1154,244)}水母捕手博览会
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.97,0:12:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只能另外再找朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It will have to be one of your other chums
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我去意已决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause my mind is set
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别决了  求你别决了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Unset it, please unset it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.69,0:13:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我得打包马上就出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll pack up my stuff and get ready to go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那些是我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, those are my clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的花生酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:19.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My peanut butter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的花生酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my peanut butter
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我的腌椰菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然要就这么走了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're leaving, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还把我腌椰菜全带走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with all my pickles
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以后再也不会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the end of me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,being here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.97,0:13:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们的计划呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about all our plans?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上八点  叫醒派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"8:00 a.m., wake up Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上九点  跟派大星吃海草哥麦片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"9:00 a.m., eat Kelpo with Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上十点  跟派大星刷牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"10:00 a.m., brush teeth with Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下午一点  盯派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,1:00 p.m., stare at Patrick"
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有谁来跟我一起做事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's going to do all that with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.77,0:13:51.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  大势不可挡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:51.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, there's no stopping the unstoppable
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.51,0:13:55.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星以后永远都不会再
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:55.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick Star will live no more, forever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住在裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:56.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可要是你不是派大星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what if you weren't Patrick Star?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是派大星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not Patrick Star?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是派大星没错  但马上你就不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:07.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are Patrick Star, but you won't be for long
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you go, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.42,0:14:11.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都认不出来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:11.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one will know it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:19.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  墨镜挺酷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, cool shades
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  那套伪装不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Pat, that disguise didn't work
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得再加把劲才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to have to try harder
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  多谢你相助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, thanks, old SpongeBob, for your help
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽管竭尽了全力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a noble effort
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜都是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but alas, all in vain
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no use
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.85,0:14:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须得走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must leave
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  石头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, rock
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, coral
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  海草
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, seaweed
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜没能想出来哪件衣服更好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad we couldn't come up with a better costume
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, sky
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要你戴上那个海草  就会是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With that seaweed on your head, you could be
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.63,0:15:00.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.16,0:15:00.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:00.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就会是海草怪物哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:03.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could be Mr. Seaweed Monster Man
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从此就能幸福快乐住在裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And live happily forever after in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  已经有个海草怪物哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, there already is a Mr. Seaweed Monster Man
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.10,0:15:13.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.10,0:15:13.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当不了怪物就当不了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you can't be a monster
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你头顶那株草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that vegetation on your head
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我想到可以把你扮成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,give me an idea of what you can be
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.92,0:15:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打扮好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all set
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出来吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on out, Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(890,884)}裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:35.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And hello, lady
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.57,0:15:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伪装成功了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The disguise is working, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.30,0:15:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都没跟我说过自己交了女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you never told me you had a girlfriend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是他女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not his girlfriend
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是派
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.24,0:15:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tricia
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派小妹  派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patricia, Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.43,0:15:57.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  你女朋友不丑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:57.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bro, your girlfriend is not ugly
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拉里  她其实不是我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, Larry, she's not my girlfriend
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.33,0:16:00.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只是个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:00.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She's just a
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's cool, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用给我介绍你女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to explain your girlfriend to me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可她不是我女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But she's not my girlfriend
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你何必要站这边找我说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know why you're standing here talking to me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要跟你女朋友闲聊才对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you could be talking to your girlfriend
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧  派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你新交上了个女朋友  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:16.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on the new girlfriend, dude
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.72,0:16:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  现在可不适合周日散步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, this is not the time for a Sunday stroll
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.17,0:16:21.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time for work
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王两小时后才开门营业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krusty Krab doesn't open for another two hours
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.42,0:16:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开门根本就没太早这回事  我的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There'll be no such thing as opening too early, me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse us, Miss
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你朋友哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:39.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, who's your friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  这位是派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, this is Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直是最美的芳名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The most beautiful sound I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.94,0:16:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  蟹堡王那边还缺人手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, do we need any more help
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down at The Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.40,0:16:50.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不缺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:50.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,缺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.91,0:16:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她马上就能入职
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She can start right away
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:55.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426,490)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.20,0:17:05.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敢问芳名  我身材姣好的大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:05.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And who are you, my Rubenesque beauty?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Patricia--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王新来的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,our newest Krusty Krab employee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她可真是美丽动人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, she sure is stunning
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管好客人的事就行了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just keep your eyes on the customers, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.86,0:17:25.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我给你画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:25.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I drew this for you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我说  画得可谓跟你异常相像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The likeness is uncanny if I do say so myself
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, Miss Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这餐是七号桌的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This order goes to table seven
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了你的礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And remember your manners
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,nee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,foo-nee
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是七号  派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a seven, Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.55,0:17:58.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  是你点了两份蟹堡套餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:58.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, you ordered two Krusty Meals?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我点了两份套餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did I order two meals?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Silly me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自个可没法一口气吃俩蟹堡套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly eat two Krusty Meals myself
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.99,0:18:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你多半得帮我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess you'll just have to help me finish all this food
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派小妹  虽然我们仅仅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patricia, we may have only
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相识了一小会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,known each other for a short time now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.66,0:18:23.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但我感觉咱俩已经建立了特殊的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:23.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I feel like a special connection has been made
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.67,0:18:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胃口真大啊  不过她女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quite an appetite, but she's all woman
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派小妹  跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:48.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我这名嘴章鱼的称号可不是白叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.67,0:18:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they don't call me the sizzle-lipped squid for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这周六晚上有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So are you free this Saturday night?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.99,0:18:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.12,0:19:01.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那时候要跟海绵宝宝比干瞪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the night SpongeBob and I
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are having a staring contest
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去工作  你个占便宜的懒鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to work, you goldbricking freeloader
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二一二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hut two, hut, two
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄堡没蟹就不准回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't come back until all those patties are Krabby
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然只剩咱俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:12.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now that we're alone
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周五晚上要不要来约个会  就到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how would you like to be my date Friday night to a
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那时候要跟海绵宝宝开潜艇到处飞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob and I will be flying submarines that night
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得继续蟹那个堡王了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to get back to Krusting the Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.63,0:19:26.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  他们两个为什么对我那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:26.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, why are those two so nice to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们从来没对派大星这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They were never this nice to Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's weird
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定周六晚上没空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about Saturday night?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,紧追不放的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Persistent bunch
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周天吃早午餐行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about Sunday brunch?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再次感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我都预约了两人桌  就在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I made reservations for two at
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said no
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:48.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.45,0:19:51.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:51.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.24,0:19:51.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:51.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到底哪里好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.77,0:19:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it about me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能让他们两个这么友好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that makes those two so friendly?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定跟这身伪装有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:19:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must have something to do with this disguise
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能再装下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wear this any longer
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是秘密身份暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you reveal your secret identity
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就只能离开裤头村了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:06.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll have to leave Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.79,0:20:10.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不能这样生活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:10.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just can't live like this anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经烦透了假装别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of pretending to be someone I'm not
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可爱的派小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The lovely Patricia
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回到我们身边了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has returned to us
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布个事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:23.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have an announcement to make
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在这上了一整天的班
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:26.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The entire day that I've worked here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to say
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.62,0:20:38.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:38.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to say that, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.82,0:20:39.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:39.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.51,0:20:44.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会吃掉你们盘子上面的剩菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:44.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I will eat any leftovers you leave on your plate
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.12,0:20:49.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:49.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个女服务生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Waitress
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不帮我点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna take my order?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我马上来  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就  就是那个带手提箱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Th-that's the guy with the briefcase
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就他要把我赶出镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The guy who's trying to run me out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The assassin
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要什么服务  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can I get you, sir?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我该不会在哪见过你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't I know you from somewhere?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.42,0:21:12.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:12.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速离开镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get outta town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.91,0:21:20.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们被他盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:20.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's on to us
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝不让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得先使出可怕技俩对付我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to do something horrible to me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才能把派大星赶出镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before I'll let you throw Patrick out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你忘拿传单了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You forgot your flyer
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,速速离开镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Get outta town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到美丽的晴空海岸度假区
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To beautiful Sunny Shore Resorts"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.81,0:21:36.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  他并没有要把你赶出镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:36.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, this guy wasn't trying to run you out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.05,0:21:39.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是想低价给你提供奢华假期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He just wanted to sell you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a luxury vacation at a modest price
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.40,0:21:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来我再也用不着这套伪装了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I don't need this disguise anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己得去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:50.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I need to take a shower
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我搞清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, let me get this straight
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是女的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not a woman?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.11,0:21:57.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开除你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:57.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, then you're fired
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.93,0:22:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有事就来办公室找我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.93,0:22:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If anybody needs me, I'll be in my office
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.10,0:22:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我大概会在里面待个差不多20年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for, I don't know, the next 20 years or so
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  要不要一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:06.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, what do you say we go home
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始做这单子上面的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get started on this list?
